'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #1999] on 18 April 2000 at 4:21:48 pm'!"Change Set:		TransformFixes-arDate:			18 April 2000Author:			Andreas RaabFixes for resize problems when a flexed morph has been rotated before scaling it."!!TransformationMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 4/18/2000 16:21'!extent: newExtent	| scaleFactor |	self adjustAfter:		[scaleFactor _ (self scale * newExtent r / self fullBounds extent r) max: 0.1.		self scale: (scaleFactor detentBy: 0.1 atMultiplesOf: 1.0 snap: false)]! !!TransformationMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 4/18/2000 15:53'!scaleToFit: anExtent	| scaleFactor |	scaleFactor _ self scale * (anExtent r / self fullBounds extent r).	scaleFactor _ scaleFactor < 1.0		ifTrue: [scaleFactor detentBy: 0.05 atMultiplesOf: 0.25 snap: false]		ifFalse: [scaleFactor detentBy: 0.1 atMultiplesOf: 0.5 snap: false].	self scale: ((scaleFactor min: 8.0) max: 0.1).	self extent: anExtent! !!TransformationMorph methodsFor: 'change reporting' stamp: 'ar 4/18/2000 16:07'!layoutChanged	"Recompute bounds as a result of change"	self hasSubmorphs ifTrue:		[bounds _ (transform localBoundsToGlobal:					(Rectangle merging:						(self submorphs collect: [:m | m fullBounds]))) truncated				expandBy: 1].	super layoutChanged! !